dct_title_s: Italia mit dreyen fu¨rnemesten Inseln, Corsica, Sardinia, vnd Sicilia
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. German text on verso with caption title: Italia mit den dreyen fürnemesten Inseln, Corsica, Sardinia, Sicilia, vnd andern vielen kleinen Inseln; p. xviij. Appears in a German ed. of Münster's Cosmographia, published sometime between 1544 and 1628.
